{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":117,"text":"So this is Anna Hazare,"},{"time":3769,"text":"and Anna Hazare may well be\nthe most cutting-edge"},{"time":7677,"text":"digital activist in the world today."},{"time":10914,"text":"And you wouldn't know it by looking at him."},{"time":12452,"text":"Hazare is a 77-year-old Indian \nanticorruption and social justice activist."},{"time":18099,"text":"And in 2011, he was running a big campaign"},{"time":21690,"text":"to address everyday corruption in India,"},{"time":24650,"text":"a topic that Indian elites love to ignore."},{"time":27521,"text":"So as part of this campaign,"},{"time":29103,"text":"he was using all of the traditional tactics"},{"time":31025,"text":"that a good Gandhian organizer would use."},{"time":33241,"text":"So he was on a hunger strike,"},{"time":35297,"text":"and Hazare realized through his hunger"},{"time":37822,"text":"that actually maybe this time,"},{"time":39599,"text":"in the 21st century,"},{"time":41345,"text":"a hunger strike wouldn't be enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42834,"text":"So he started playing around \nwith mobile activism."},{"time":47126,"text":"So the first thing he did \nis he said to people,"},{"time":49013,"text":"\"Okay, why don't you send me"},{"time":51084,"text":"a text message if you support"},{"time":52845,"text":"my campaign against corruption?\""},{"time":54585,"text":"So he does this, he \ngives people a short code,"},{"time":56854,"text":"and about 80,000 people do it."},{"time":59470,"text":"Okay, that's pretty respectable."},{"time":61438,"text":"But then he decides,"},{"time":62375,"text":"\"Let me tweak my tactics a little bit.\""},{"time":64495,"text":"He says, \"Why don't you leave\nme a missed call?\""},{"time":68970,"text":"Now, for those of you who have\nlived in the global South,"},{"time":72039,"text":"you'll know that missed calls"},{"time":73531,"text":"are a really critical part\nof global mobile culture."},{"time":77374,"text":"I see people nodding."},{"time":78488,"text":"People leave missed calls all the time:"},{"time":80596,"text":"If you're running late for a meeting"},{"time":82542,"text":"and you just want to let them\nknow that you're on the way,"},{"time":84848,"text":"you leave them a missed call."},{"time":86571,"text":"If you're dating someone and \nyou just want to say \"I miss you\""},{"time":88497,"text":"you leave them a missed call."},{"time":89883,"text":"So a note for a dating tip here,"},{"time":92427,"text":"in some cultures,"},{"time":93552,"text":"if you want to please your lover,"},{"time":94834,"text":"you call them and hang up.\n(Laughter)"},{"time":99335,"text":"So why do people leave missed calls?"},{"time":102690,"text":"Well, the reason of course is that"},{"time":104140,"text":"they're trying to avoid charges"},{"time":106898,"text":"associated with making calls\nand sending texts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110264,"text":"So when Hazare asked people \nto leave him a missed call,"},{"time":114320,"text":"let's have a little guess how \nmany people actually did this?"},{"time":119997,"text":"Thirty-five million."},{"time":123415,"text":"So this is one of the largest coordinated\nactions in human history."},{"time":127458,"text":"It's remarkable."},{"time":129212,"text":"And this reflects the extraordinary strength \nof the emerging Indian middle class"},{"time":133712,"text":"and the power that their\nmobile phones bring."},{"time":136684,"text":"But he used that,"},{"time":138269,"text":"Hazare ended up with this massive \nCSV file of mobile phone numbers,"},{"time":142488,"text":"and he used that to deploy"},{"time":144273,"text":"real people power on the ground"},{"time":146269,"text":"to get hundreds of thousands of\npeople out on the streets in Delhi"},{"time":149683,"text":"to make a national point of \neveryday corruption in India."},{"time":154033,"text":"It's a really striking story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156470,"text":"So this is me when I was 12 years old."},{"time":158680,"text":"I hope you see the resemblance."},{"time":160392,"text":"And I was also an activist,"},{"time":162317,"text":"and I have been an activist all my life."},{"time":164557,"text":"I had this really funny childhood"},{"time":165887,"text":"where I traipsed around the world"},{"time":167910,"text":"meeting world leaders and \nNoble prize winners,"},{"time":170704,"text":"talking about Third World debt,"},{"time":172990,"text":"as it was then called,"},{"time":174279,"text":"and demilitarization."},{"time":175813,"text":"I was a very, very serious child.\n(Laughter)"},{"time":180045,"text":"And back then,"},{"time":181950,"text":"in the early '90s,"},{"time":183384,"text":"I had a very cutting-edge\ntech tool of my own:"},{"time":187214,"text":"the fax."},{"time":189466,"text":"And the fax was the \ntool of my activism."},{"time":191644,"text":"And at that time, it was the best way"},{"time":193202,"text":"to get a message to a lot of people"},{"time":195097,"text":"all at once."},{"time":197535,"text":"I'll give you one example of a fax\ncampaign that I ran."},{"time":199981,"text":"It was the eve of the Gulf War"},{"time":202077,"text":"and I organized a global campaign \nto flood the hotel,"},{"time":205628,"text":"the Intercontinental in Geneva,"},{"time":207109,"text":"where James Baker and Tariq Aziz"},{"time":208664,"text":"were meeting on the eve of the war,"},{"time":210588,"text":"and I thought if I could \nflood them with faxes,"},{"time":212972,"text":"we'll stop the war."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214050,"text":"Well, unsurprisingly,"},{"time":216243,"text":"that campaign was wholly unsuccessful."},{"time":219834,"text":"There are lots of reasons for that,"},{"time":221488,"text":"but there's no doubt that \none sputtering fax machine"},{"time":223973,"text":"in Geneva was a little bit\nof a bandwidth constraint"},{"time":227300,"text":"in terms of the ability to \nget a message to lots of people."},{"time":230142,"text":"And so, I went on to \ndiscover some better tools."},{"time":234172,"text":"I cofounded Avaaz, which uses the \nInternet to mobilize people"},{"time":236814,"text":"and now has almost \n40 million members,"},{"time":239412,"text":"and I now run Purpose, which \nis a home for these kinds of"},{"time":241972,"text":"technology-powered movements."},{"time":244268,"text":"So what's the moral of this story?"},{"time":246088,"text":"Is the moral of this story,\n"},{"time":247596,"text":"you know what, the fax is kind of\neclipsed by the mobile phone?"},{"time":252705,"text":"This is another story of \ntech-determinism?"},{"time":254935,"text":"Well, I would argue that there's \nactually more to it than that."},{"time":258125,"text":"I'd argue that in the last 20 years,"},{"time":260798,"text":"something more fundamental has changed\n"},{"time":263036,"text":"than just new tech."},{"time":264741,"text":"I would argue that there has\nbeen a fundamental shift"},{"time":267561,"text":"in the balance of power"},{"time":269709,"text":"in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271228,"text":"You ask any activist how \nto understand the world,"},{"time":273145,"text":"and they'll say,\n\"Look at where the power is,"},{"time":275619,"text":"who has it, how it's shifting.\""},{"time":278077,"text":"And I think we all sense that \nsomething big is happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281079,"text":"So Henry Timms and I —"},{"time":283523,"text":"Henry's a fellow movement builder —"},{"time":285371,"text":"got talking one day and \nwe started to think,"},{"time":287273,"text":"how can we make sense of this new world?"},{"time":289274,"text":"How can we describe it and give"},{"time":290463,"text":"it a framework that makes it more useful?"},{"time":292906,"text":"Because we realized that many"},{"time":294136,"text":"of the lessons that we were\ndiscovering in movements"},{"time":296950,"text":"actually applied all over the world"},{"time":299657,"text":"in many sectors of our society."},{"time":301779,"text":"So I want to introduce you to\nthis framework:"},{"time":303656,"text":"Old power, meet new power."},{"time":305876,"text":"And I want to talk to you about\nwhat new power is today."},{"time":309307,"text":"New power is the deployment"},{"time":311271,"text":"of mass participation \nand peer coordination —"},{"time":314460,"text":"these are the two key elements —"},{"time":316102,"text":"to create change and shift outcomes."},{"time":318599,"text":"And we see new power all around us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321687,"text":"This is Beppe Grillo"},{"time":322971,"text":"he was a populist Italian blogger"},{"time":325116,"text":"who, with a minimal political apparatus\nand only some online tools,"},{"time":328536,"text":"won more than 25 percent of the vote"},{"time":331034,"text":"in recent Italian elections."},{"time":333455,"text":"This is Airbnb,"},{"time":334817,"text":"which in just a few years"},{"time":336566,"text":"has radically disrupted the hotel industry"},{"time":338728,"text":"without owning a single\nsquare foot of real estate."},{"time":341646,"text":"This is Kickstarter,"},{"time":343001,"text":"which we know has raised over a billion dollars"},{"time":345898,"text":"from more than five million people."},{"time":348319,"text":"Now, we're familiar with all of these models."},{"time":350249,"text":"But what's striking is the commonalities,"},{"time":353450,"text":"the structural features of \nthese new models"},{"time":355576,"text":"and how they differ from old power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357725,"text":"Let's look a little bit at this."},{"time":359394,"text":"Old power is held like a currency."},{"time":362552,"text":"New power works like a current."},{"time":364531,"text":"Old power is held by a few."},{"time":367033,"text":"New power isn't held by a few,\nit's made by many."},{"time":370473,"text":"Old power is all about download,"},{"time":372980,"text":"and new power uploads."},{"time":374706,"text":"And you see a whole set of \ncharacteristics that you can trace,"},{"time":377240,"text":"whether it's in media or \npolitics or education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380356,"text":"So we've talked a little bit \nabout what new power is."},{"time":382422,"text":"Let's, for a second, talk about \nwhat new power isn't."},{"time":385587,"text":"New power is not your Facebook page."},{"time":389383,"text":"I assure you that having a \nsocial media strategy"},{"time":392208,"text":"can enable you to do just as much download"},{"time":394756,"text":"as you used to do when you had the radio."},{"time":397618,"text":"Just ask Syrian dictator Bashar al-Assad,"},{"time":401146,"text":"I assure you that his Facebook page"},{"time":402888,"text":"has not embraced the power\nof participation."},{"time":407015,"text":"New power is not inherently positive."},{"time":410413,"text":"In fact, this isn't an normative\nargument that we're making,"},{"time":412702,"text":"there are many good things \nabout new power,"},{"time":414514,"text":"but it can produce bad outcomes."},{"time":416331,"text":"More participation, more peer coordination,"},{"time":418336,"text":"sometimes distorts outcomes"},{"time":420123,"text":"and there are some things,"},{"time":421198,"text":"like things, for example, \nin the medical profession"},{"time":423297,"text":"that we want new power \nto get nowhere near."},{"time":426293,"text":"And thirdly, new power is not\nthe inevitable victor."},{"time":429296,"text":"In fact, unsurprisingly,"},{"time":430875,"text":"as many of these new power\nmodels get to scale,"},{"time":433864,"text":"what you see is this massive pushback"},{"time":436334,"text":"from the forces of old power."},{"time":438083,"text":"Just look at this really \ninteresting epic struggle"},{"time":440292,"text":"going on right now between \nEdward Snowden and the NSA."},{"time":444675,"text":"You'll note that only one of \nthe two people on this slide"},{"time":447059,"text":"is currently in exile."},{"time":449238,"text":"And so, it's not at all clear"},{"time":450653,"text":"that new power will be \nthe inevitable victor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452743,"text":"That said, keep one thing in mind:\n"},{"time":455686,"text":"We're at the beginning of a\nvery steep curve."},{"time":458575,"text":"So you think about some of \nthese new power models, right?"},{"time":460216,"text":"These were just like someone's"},{"time":462328,"text":"garage idea a few years ago,"},{"time":464874,"text":"and now they're disrupting \nentire industries."},{"time":468010,"text":"And so, what's interesting\nabout new power,"},{"time":470679,"text":"is the way it feeds\non itself."},{"time":472695,"text":"Once you have an experience of new power,"},{"time":474719,"text":"you tend to expect and \nwant more of it."},{"time":476909,"text":"So let's say you've used a\npeer-to-peer lending platform"},{"time":479789,"text":"like Lending Tree or Prosper,"},{"time":482323,"text":"then you've figured out that\nyou don't need the bank,"},{"time":484607,"text":"and who wants the bank, right?"},{"time":486544,"text":"And so, that experience tends \nto embolden you"},{"time":488982,"text":"it tends to make you want\nmore participation"},{"time":491919,"text":"across more aspects of your life."},{"time":494264,"text":"And what this gives rise to is"},{"time":495809,"text":"a set of values."},{"time":497380,"text":"We talked about the models"},{"time":498690,"text":"that new power has engendered —"},{"time":500284,"text":"the Airbnbs, the Kickstarters."},{"time":502116,"text":"What about the values?"},{"time":503645,"text":"And this is an early sketch"},{"time":505315,"text":"at what new power values look like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507878,"text":"New power values prize\ntransparency above all else."},{"time":511009,"text":"It's almost a religious \nbelief in transparency,"},{"time":513231,"text":"a belief that if you shine \na light on something,"},{"time":515495,"text":"it will be better."},{"time":516926,"text":"And remember that in the 20th \ncentury, this was not at all true."},{"time":519676,"text":"People thought that gentlemen\nshould sit behind closed doors"},{"time":522643,"text":"and make comfortable agreements."},{"time":524925,"text":"New power values of informal,\nnetworked governance."},{"time":528330,"text":"New power folks would never \nhave invented the U.N. today,"},{"time":530974,"text":"for better or worse."},{"time":532807,"text":"New power values participation,"},{"time":534522,"text":"and new power is all about do-it-yourself."},{"time":537317,"text":"In fact, what's interesting \nabout new power"},{"time":538806,"text":"is that it eschews some of \nthe professionalization"},{"time":542519,"text":"and specialization that was"},{"time":543994,"text":"all the rage in the 20th century."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546384,"text":"So what's interesting about these"},{"time":548194,"text":"new power values and these\nnew power models"},{"time":550160,"text":"is what they mean for organizations."},{"time":552455,"text":"So we've spent a bit of time thinking,"},{"time":554963,"text":"how can we plot organizations"},{"time":557229,"text":"on a two-by-two where, essentially,"},{"time":559493,"text":"we look at new power values"},{"time":561549,"text":"and new power models"},{"time":562813,"text":"and see where different people sit?"},{"time":564614,"text":"We started with a U.S. analysis,"},{"time":566503,"text":"and let me show you \nsome interesting findings."},{"time":568879,"text":"So the first is Apple."},{"time":570858,"text":"In this framework, we actually\ndescribed Apple"},{"time":573393,"text":"as an old power company."},{"time":575515,"text":"That's because the ideology,"},{"time":577169,"text":"the governing ideology of Apple"},{"time":579457,"text":"is the ideology of the perfectionist"},{"time":582331,"text":"product designer in Cupertino."},{"time":584355,"text":"It's absolutely about that beautiful, \nperfect thing descending upon us"},{"time":588427,"text":"in perfection."},{"time":589778,"text":"And it does not value, as a \ncompany, transparency."},{"time":592401,"text":"In fact, it's very secretive."},{"time":594064,"text":"Now, Apple is one of the most\nsuccesful companies in the world."},{"time":596890,"text":"So this shows that you can\n"},{"time":598262,"text":"still pursue a successful \nold power strategy."},{"time":600951,"text":"But one can argue that there's \nreal vulnerabilites in that model."},{"time":603921,"text":"I think another interesting comparison"},{"time":605945,"text":"is that of the Obama campaign"},{"time":608122,"text":"versus the Obama presidency."},{"time":611238,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":618700,"text":"Now, I like President Obama,"},{"time":620447,"text":"but he ran with new \npower at his back, right?"},{"time":624403,"text":"And he said to people,\n"},{"time":626230,"text":"we are the ones we've\nbeen waiting for."},{"time":628203,"text":"And he used crowdfunding"},{"time":629654,"text":"to power a campaign."},{"time":630865,"text":"But when he got into office,"},{"time":632266,"text":"he governed like more or less \nall the other presidents did."},{"time":635458,"text":"And this is a really interesting trend,"},{"time":637822,"text":"is when new power gets powerful,"},{"time":639820,"text":"what happens?\n"},{"time":641391,"text":"So this is a framework you \nshould look at"},{"time":643155,"text":"and think about where your\nown organization"},{"time":644647,"text":"sits on it."},{"time":645611,"text":"And think about where it\nshould be \n"},{"time":647184,"text":"in five or 10 years."},{"time":648732,"text":"So what do you do if you're old power?"},{"time":651197,"text":"Well, if you're there \nthinking, in old power,"},{"time":654162,"text":"this won't happen to us."},{"time":656062,"text":"Then just look at the Wikipedia\nentry for Encyclopædia Britannica."},{"time":661229,"text":"Let me tell you, it's a very sad read."}]},{"cues":[{"time":663625,"text":"But if you are old power,"},{"time":665044,"text":"the most important thing you \ncan do is to occupy yourself"},{"time":668837,"text":"before others occupy you,"},{"time":671491,"text":"before you are occupied."},{"time":672819,"text":"Imagine that a group\nof your biggest skeptics"},{"time":675592,"text":"are camped in the heart\nof your organization"},{"time":677944,"text":"asking the toughest questions"},{"time":679823,"text":"and they can see everything\ninside of your organization."},{"time":682751,"text":"And ask them, would they \nlike what they see"},{"time":685501,"text":"and should our model change?"},{"time":687776,"text":"What about if you're new power?\n"},{"time":689639,"text":"Is new power kind of just \nriding the wave to glory?"},{"time":692273,"text":"I would argue no."},{"time":693753,"text":"I would argue that there\nare some very real challenges"},{"time":695709,"text":"to new power in this nascent phase."},{"time":697401,"text":"Let's stick with the Occupy Wall Street\nexample for a moment."},{"time":700903,"text":"Occupy was this incredible example \nof new power,"},{"time":703893,"text":"the purest example of new power."},{"time":705736,"text":"And yet, it failed to consolidate."},{"time":708267,"text":"So the energy that it created"},{"time":710164,"text":"was great for the meme phase,"},{"time":711605,"text":"but they were so committed to participation,"},{"time":714406,"text":"that they never got anything done."},{"time":716040,"text":"And in fact that model"},{"time":717831,"text":"means that the challenge for new power is:"},{"time":720623,"text":"how do you use institutional power"},{"time":723162,"text":"without being institutionalized?\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":725233,"text":"One the other end of the spectra is Uber."},{"time":727866,"text":"Uber is an amazing,"},{"time":729250,"text":"highly scalable new power model."},{"time":731303,"text":"That network is getting denser and denser"},{"time":733329,"text":"by the day."},{"time":734589,"text":"But what's really interesting \nabout Uber is"},{"time":736748,"text":"it hasn't really adopted new power values."},{"time":740489,"text":"This is a real quote from \nthe Uber CEO recently:"},{"time":744561,"text":"He says, \"Once we get rid of the dude \nin the car\" — he means drivers —"},{"time":749009,"text":"\"Uber will be cheaper.\""},{"time":752901,"text":"Now, new power models\nlive and die"},{"time":755876,"text":"by the strength of their networks."},{"time":758058,"text":"By whether the drivers and the consumers\n"},{"time":759991,"text":"who use the service actually believe in it."},{"time":762332,"text":"Because they're not an exercise \nof top-down perfectionism,"},{"time":765833,"text":"they are about the network."},{"time":767781,"text":"And so, the challenge,"},{"time":769477,"text":"and this is why it's in\nno way surprising,"},{"time":771727,"text":"is that Uber's drivers \nare now unionizing."},{"time":775983,"text":"It's extraordinary."},{"time":777583,"text":"Uber's drivers are turning on Uber."},{"time":779872,"text":"And the challenge for Uber —"},{"time":781166,"text":"this isn't an easy situation for them —"},{"time":783093,"text":"is that they are locked into\na broader superstrcuture"},{"time":786389,"text":"that is really old power."},{"time":788074,"text":"They've raised more than a billion \ndollars in the capital markets."},{"time":791082,"text":"Those markets expect a financial return,"},{"time":793610,"text":"and they way you get a financial return"},{"time":795527,"text":"is by squeezing and squeezing"},{"time":797924,"text":"your users and your drivers"},{"time":800169,"text":"for more and more value"},{"time":801464,"text":"and giving that value to your investors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803931,"text":"So the big question about the future \nof new power, in my view, is:"},{"time":807534,"text":"Will that old power just emerge?\n"},{"time":810093,"text":"So will new power elites just become"},{"time":811876,"text":"old power and squeeze?"},{"time":813765,"text":"Or will that new power\nbase bite back?"},{"time":816378,"text":"Will the next big Uber"},{"time":818139,"text":"be co-owned by Uber drivers?"},{"time":820519,"text":"And I think this going \nto be a very interesting"},{"time":823302,"text":"structural question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825204,"text":"Finally, think about new power"},{"time":828486,"text":"being more than just an"},{"time":830853,"text":"entity that scales things \n"},{"time":832489,"text":"that make us have slightly \nbetter consumer experiences."},{"time":836205,"text":"My call to action for new power"},{"time":838371,"text":"is to not be an island."},{"time":840779,"text":"We have major structural\nproblems in the world today"},{"time":843935,"text":"that could benefit enormously"},{"time":846191,"text":"from the kinds of mass participation"},{"time":848505,"text":"and peer coordination"},{"time":849842,"text":"that these new power players"},{"time":851570,"text":"know so well how to generate."},{"time":853966,"text":"And we badly need them to \nturn their energies and their power"},{"time":857479,"text":"to big, what economists might call"},{"time":860703,"text":"public goods problems,"},{"time":862276,"text":"that are often beyond markets"},{"time":864322,"text":"where investors can easily be found."},{"time":866332,"text":"And I think if we can do that,"},{"time":868222,"text":"we might be able to fundamentally change"},{"time":871207,"text":"not only human beings' sense of \ntheir own agency and power —"},{"time":874738,"text":"because I think that's the most\nwonderful thing about new power,"},{"time":877596,"text":"is that people feel more powerful —"},{"time":880348,"text":"but we might also be able to change"},{"time":882129,"text":"the way we relate to each other"},{"time":883892,"text":"and the way we relate to \nauthority and institutions."},{"time":887003,"text":"And to me, that's absolutely"},{"time":889051,"text":"worth trying for."},{"time":890622,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":891718,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}